column5: Does anybody know of a supplier based from ontario that sells attwood boat seats? There are places online to order, but they are all in the states and I dont really want to pay for duty and brokerage. Thanks in advance.
the fishin hole  They should be able to help you out with your needs
They cant get them. Thanks though!
Are they for a bass boat?
I ordered mine last year from Whitby Marina. Had it in the next day.
I sell them,I can do an order by phone,just give me a part #.
proctor marine has em i think
no for my 14.5ft princecraft deep v.
I tried both the above mentioned places and no dice. Whity marina says that they dont even have a store. Thanks though!
